Stand O’Food® City: Virtual Frenzy will take you to a new level of food mastery! Hurry to get a taste of this delicious update!

OVER 170 NEW QUESTS – Can you tackle them all? Get them while they are HOT!
24 NEW COLLECTIONS – Get ready for big challenges and even bigger rewards as you expand your burger empire!
NEW FARM – Now you can cultivate shrimp for new seafood dishes.
NEW MECHANICS – Enjoy new mastering levels and new opportunities to make money!
TOP 1,000 PLAYERS RATINGS – Do you have what it takes to join this elite group?

Join the G5 email list and be the first to know about sales, news and game releases! www.g5e.com/e-mail
